# Set in Render → Environment (never commit real secrets).

# --- CORS ---
# If you OMIT this, the API defaults to FRONTEND_ORIGIN=* (all sites can call the API).
# That is OK for debugging; for production, set your real Vercel URL:
# FRONTEND_ORIGIN=https://youtube-video-jade.vercel.app
# Multiple frontends: comma-separated, no spaces, no trailing slashes:
# FRONTEND_ORIGIN=https://app1.vercel.app,https://app2.vercel.app

# --- YouTube (optional) ---
# Only if many videos return 503 / "sign in" / bot errors — paste Cookie from a logged-in browser (private use).
# YOUTUBE_COOKIE=

# --- Rare ---
# FFMPEG_LOCATION=   # only if ffmpeg not on PATH (Docker image already has /usr/bin)
